data.description: Location location location on this gorgeous Bluewater Rise home! Nestled in the back of the neighborhood on a double cul-de-sac street- this house sits on one of the largest (0.46 acres)and most private lots in the neighborhood! Just built in 2021, and still has that New House feeling! Featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, beautiful great room (dining/ living combination), eat at kitchen island, pantry, laundry room, covered patio and an additional wooden deck and uncovered stone patio. You will love the stunning laminate flooring throughout the first floor and granite countertops in the kitchen! Master bedroom features a tray ceiling and expansive walk in closet. Master bath has dual vanities, walk in  shower and separate tub! Complete with a two car garage for plenty of storage! Don't miss this opportunity to own this amazing house in the well sought after Bluewater Rise subdivision!
